{"type":null,"faqId":19329,"title":"屏幕自动黑屏","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.s1{display: inline-block; text-indent: 0; min-width: 0.3048611in;}\n.s2{font-weight:bold;}\n.p1{text-indent:-0.2951389in;margin-left:1.4763889in;margin-top:0.055555556in;margin-bottom:0.055555556in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10pt;}\n.p2{margin-left:1.4763889in;margin-top:0.055555556in;margin-bottom:0.055555556in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10pt;}\n.p3{margin-left:1.4763889in;margin-top:0.22222222in;margin-bottom:0.055555556in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;keep-with-next.within-page:always;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10pt;}\n.p4{text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;keep-with-next.within-page:always;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.p5{text-indent:0.29166666in;margin-left:1.18125in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10pt;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n <span>通话过程中屏幕自动黑屏。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>这是正常现象。是由于手机听筒靠近头部时，听筒附近的接近光传感器被遮挡，屏幕自动关闭，进入省电模式。当手机离开头部，屏幕自动点亮。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>为了保证手机的正常使用，请注意不要用手机套或其他物体遮挡听筒附近的屏幕。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n <span>运行某些不兼容的第三方应用程序时屏幕黑屏。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>请卸载该应用程序或备份重要数据后将手机恢复出厂设置。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n <span>同时运行过多应用程序可能会导致屏幕黑屏。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>彻底关闭后台暂时不需要的应用程序：在</span><span class=\"s2\">设置</span><span>中的</span><span class=\"s2\">全部设置</span><span>页签下，点击</span><span class=\"s2\">应用</span><span>&gt;</span><span class=\"s2\">管理应用</span><span>，点击您要关闭的应用程序，然后点击</span><span class=\"s2\">停止</span><span>，即可关闭此程序。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >图1-1<a name=\"_Toc408418073\"></a>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p4\">\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=64224\" style=\"width:5.0in;height:1.9465277in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p class=\"p5\">\n<span>* 图示仅供参考，具体操作请以手机实际界面为准。</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":134,"faqType":"硬件与外观","useful":0,"unUseful":1,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"2470","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Hardware-Appearance","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1422608222000,"seriesProductName":"G628-TL00","visitedTimes":214,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":null,"avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}